name: Compiled Create ML Model
summary: An MLMODELC file is a compiled machine learning model created by Apple Xcode . Xcode creates an MLMODELC file when a developer packages an app development project that includes an .MLMODEL file. The MLMODELC file is stored within the packaged app (an .APP or .IPA file).

open.note: Open with an associated app listed below.
